column12: Linear Regression model - provides an equation to use to predict the prices.
Equation: Consumer MSRP = -5,269 + 8,413 x Carat + 158.1 x Cut + 454 x Clarity
Equation: Company Price at 70% off MSRP = above formula * 0.3
